Description: Screenshot snipping tool for COSMIC Desktop / Wayland
 CosmicSnip is a Windows Snipping Tool clone built natively for the COSMIC
 Desktop Environment on Pop!_OS 24.04. It captures the screen via the XDG
 Desktop Portal, lets you drag to select a region, and opens an annotation
 editor with pen, highlighter, arrow, and rectangle tools.
 .
 Features:
  * Instant fullscreen capture with drag-to-select region
  * Annotation tools: pen, highlighter, arrow, rectangle
  * Copy to Wayland clipboard (Ctrl+C)
  * Save As dialog with full path control (Ctrl+S)
  * Multi-monitor aware
  * Native Wayland — no X11 required
